meanings.definition: A type of fuel injection system in which multiple fuel jets are used to inject fuel into the combustion chamber.
meanings.sent1: The mechanic explained how the multijet system works in cars.
meanings.sent2: The multijet technology has improved the efficiency of modern engines.
meanings.sent3: I wish my coffee machine had a multijet to inject the milk perfectly.
meanings.sent4: Her words were like a multijet of emotions, hitting me all at once.
meanings.sent5: The multijet of colors in the painting made it stand out from the rest.

meanings.definition: A type of printer that uses multiple jets to spray ink onto paper.
meanings.sent1: The office upgraded to a multijet printer for faster printing.
meanings.sent2: The multijet printer produced high-quality images for the presentation.
meanings.sent3: The multijet printer danced across the paper, creating a masterpiece.
meanings.sent4: Her ideas flowed from her mind to the paper like a multijet of creativity.
meanings.sent5: The multijet of ink added depth to the printed photographs.
